  Aminu Ado Bayero has been announced as the new Emir of Kano. The move comes a few hours after Muhammed Sanusi II was dethroned by the Kano State Government. A source at the Kano Emirate Council disclosed that the former monarch will take abode in an undisclosed town in Nasarawa State following his removal. 



